' Question answered: who performs each step in a multi-actor approval process, and where does it branch?
' Declare the first swimlane before start so the start node lands in a named lane.
|Customer|
start
:Submit purchase request;
|Manager|
:Review request;
if (Approved?) then (yes)
  |Finance|
  :Issue purchase order;
  |Vendor|
  :Fulfill order;
else (else)
  |Customer|
  :Receive rejection notice;
endif
|Customer|
:Close request;
stop
